Articles.Content:
@SpaceplaneAddict - I didn't get a chance to test your craft yesterday. Will try to get a run in later today.

I'm somewhat concerned about the radiators and solar panels you added. We'll see how it goes.

Happy landings!

@Starhawk - your the pilot in command if you feel the plane is not airworthy feel free to remove them. However I can not allow any additions or off sets. I get done with work early today as well so I may beat you to the punch ![;)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif)

Oh forgot to mention I loved the monoprop placement on the stingray. No risk of blowing up and control was wonderful I am definitely stealing this design practice for now on.

